### Variables base
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@username = admin
@password = Admin123*

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/system/health

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Token
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### Usuario actual
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Contextos operativos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/contextos-operativos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reporte de ventas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reportes/ventas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reporte de caja
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reportes/caja
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Historial de reportes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reportes/historial
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar ventas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reportes/ventas/exportar?formato=xlsx
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar caja
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reportes/caja/exportar?formato=pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
